      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration only. No additional load configurations (e.g., axial compression, torsion) were included in this validation activity. Environmental conditions (ambient temperature, humidity) were documented and controlled. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given the focused scope of the COU, which is limited to F1717 compression-bending only.",
