      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in the FEA model replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry and loading point locations as measured from the physical test fixture. Applied displacement rate in the model corresponds to the quasi-static rate used in testing. Differences in fixture compliance were characterized and shown to have less than 0.5% effect on predicted QoIs. Achieved level meets required level."
