    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3 due to testing under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration. This shortfall is accepted given the COU is explicitly scoped to F1717 static compression-bending only, and the three pre-specified QoIs all satisfy quantitative acceptance bounds across N=11 constructs at two independent laboratories. The overall credibility of the simulation evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
